</ResponseField>

## Notes

- Returns empty array if no bookmarks exist.
- Each bookmark includes the full job details.

## Error Responses

### 401 Unauthorized

Returned when authentication is missing.

```json
{
  "success": false,
  "error": {
    "message": "Unauthorized",
    "statusCode": 401,
    "timestamp": "2026-02-22T15:01:29.639Z",
    "path": "/jobs/bookmark",
    "method": "GET"
  }
}
```

## Example

```bash
curl -X GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/jobs/bookmark \
  -H "Authorization: Bearer <token>"
```
</file>

