```json
{
  "success": false,
  "error": {
    "message": "Invalid file type. Only PDF, DOC, and DOCX files are allowed.",
    "statusCode": 400,
    "timestamp": "2026-02-17T08:00:00.000Z",
    "path": "/cv/presigned-url",
    "method": "POST"
  }
}
```

## Next Steps

1. Use the `uploadUrl` to upload your file (see [Upload CV File](/api-reference/cv/upload-cv-file))
2. After uploading, confirm the upload (see [Confirm CV Upload](/api-reference/cv/confirm-cv-upload))

<Warning>
  **URL Expiration**: The presigned URL expires after 1 hour. If you don't upload the file within
  this time, you'll need to request a new URL.
</Warning>
</file>

